                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-393" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SAVAGE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Whitechapel-road. I lost this flute two months ago—it has my mark on it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350817-name-394" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-394" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
