                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable S</hi> 180.) I found this flute at Mr. Pige's—I found the duplicate in the prisoner's house, with a great many more.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350817-name-395" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-395" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
