                        <interp inst="t18350817-name-395" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN CHAPMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I came from Mr. Pige's a pawnbroker. I did not take in the flure, but this duplicate was given for it.</p>
               <p>The prisoners put in a written defence, stating that Bromley had com<lb></lb>mitted several felonies, and had cohabited with their daughter, but upon their discovering his character they had turned him out of doors.</p>
